# Claude Code Starter Kit — crontab example
#
# Schedules daily-reflection via system crontab.
# Install: crontab crontab.example  (or crontab -e to add manually)
#
# Note: claude CLI must be in PATH.
#       Use absolute path (/usr/local/bin/claude) if PATH differs.

# Daily reflection at 21:43 weekdays
43 21 * * 1-5 cd /path/to/your/project && claude -p "Run the daily-reflection skill to review today's work and update CLAUDE.md."

# Logging: set MAILTO="" or redirect to a log file: >> ~/.claude/reflection-cron.log 2>&1
